  <p>Armoured combat also called buhurt is a full contact team sport in period style armour with safety rules and marshals It blends grappling striking clinch work and teamwork</p>
  <h2>Is it safe</h2>
  <p>We follow recognized safety standards require helmets and padding and coach good control Beginners start with soft gear</p>
  <h2>What you need to start</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Comfortable athletic clothes and water</li>
    <li>Soft kit or loaner gear if available</li>
    <li>Positive attitude</li>
  </ul>
